  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2 style="text-align: left;">Active Family Holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13101437/families-hero.jpg" alt="family holidays in Europe" data-udi="umb://media/b154604d56a5408b812a882c268fcd57" /></p>
<p>Step into a family holiday where each day is an invitation to explore, play and discover the great outdoors.</p>
<p>Our family holidays are all about adventure. Spend time together exploring the trails and forests, seek out summit playgrounds for some thrill-seeking fun, or burn off some energy on tree-top trails and bike parks.</p>
<p>You'll be making memories that will outlive any souvenir.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284}" title="Deals" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View 2025 Deals</a> <a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e4d461de63a64a9793c59e417f5c5eb2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d461de63a64a9793c59e417f5c5eb2}" title="Kids Fly Free"><img src="/media/13109617/kids-fly-free-desktop-banner.jpg" alt="family holidays deal" data-udi="umb://media/6a90ec7405ec421088bae90114abd374" /></a></p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Family Holidays With Us</h3>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Family Adventures</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13090580/italy-lake-family-board-walk314x193.jpg" alt="Summer family holiday Europe" data-udi="umb://media/9e293f511adc405ba219e42c63f8a0f7" /></p>
Say goodbye to screens and hello to the great outdoors – scale walls, pedal trails, and make waves with watersports.</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Family Friendly Walks</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094641/adobestock_573084073.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="family friendly walks" data-udi="umb://media/da27d6c6041442d68c5044360fef9958" /></p>
<p><span>Explore family-friendly walks with wildlife spotting, mountain adventure parks, and playgrounds to keep everyone happy.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Choice Always Included</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13105539/morzine_e14_cc_dsc6281.jpg" alt="family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/332198cc7a28454ea0f9e0edcb761a57" /></p>
<p>Pick from a huge range of family friendly places to stay across handpicked destinations, with plane or train travel options to boot.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Our Family Holiday Destinations</h2>
<p><a href="#austria" data-anchor="#austria">Austria</a> | <a href="#italy" data-anchor="#italy">Italy</a> | <a href="#switzerland" data-anchor="#switzerland">Switzerland</a> | <a href="#france" data-anchor="#france">France</a> | <a href="#slovenia" data-anchor="#slovenia">Slovenia</a> | <a href="#andorra" data-anchor="#andorra">Andorra</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">We’ve handpicked the best resorts in Europe for family holidays. Whether you want to walk through the mountains, explore the countryside, or enjoy a fun water sports activity, there’s something for everyone.</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105465/adobestock_68721568.jpg" alt="Austria family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/13164d7918034402992bceae49a61172" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2 id="austria" class="c-card__content">Austria Family Holidays</h2>
<div class="c-card__content">From mountain play areas, enchanted forests, and thrilling theme parks to wildlife trails, high ropes courses, and dedicated biking zones, there's adventure for everyone in Austria.</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">All Austria Holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/ec516f6e2eea4e73becff7970aed349e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ec516f6e2eea4e73becff7970aed349e}" title="Austria" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Austria Deals</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Our Top Family Resorts in Austria</h3>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105469/adobestock_384417002.jpg" alt="Mayrhofen family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/05ad18dca7b5486294664458fee5bd41" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Explore mountains, bike paths, family-friendly walks, and much more. Thrill-seekers can tackle high rope courses, or cool off at the adventure pool with slides and a summer toboggan run.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/13d40418b4da40d795c1847c52c88cea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13d40418b4da40d795c1847c52c88cea}" title="Neuhaus Zillertal Resort">Neuhaus Zillertal Resort</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Mayrhofen</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105470/alpbach-shutterstock-2.jpg" alt="alpbach family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/1aba470fca604a3a8f84d3081a1b3961" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4}" title="Alpbach">Alpbach</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Alpbach offers fun for all ages. Young families will love the mountain play areas, family trails, and a thrilling theme park. Alpbachtal card included for free lifts, buses, and swimming.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/7e43ab133b364827985c5c801c1617c0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e43ab133b364827985c5c801c1617c0}" title="Hotel Böglerhof">Hotel Böglerhof</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3da7b34473447c58a08fb31b2c5a7f4}" title="Alpbach" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Alpbach</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105471/saalbach_austria_adobestock_111608798.jpg" alt="saalbach hinterglemm family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/58e45897dcae49d7a4f0719508c85608" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b}" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach Hinterglemm</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Discover wildlife trails, high-ropes, playgrounds, mini golf, a thrilling jump park, treetop trails and more. Joker card included for free lifts and family-friendly attractions.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/cd318f0b6b664b1b9e19cfaefeca536e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cd318f0b6b664b1b9e19cfaefeca536e}" title="Gardenhotel Theresia (Hinterglemm)">Gardenhotel Theresia</a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b}" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Saalbach Hinterglemm</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105484/town-of-menaggio.jpg" alt="italy family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/1098e42ae6cc4484ba2fc9b195418208" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2 id="italy" class="c-card__content">Italy Family Holidays</h2>
<div class="c-card__content">Italy is a paradise for family adventures! In Selva, embrace mountain fun and adventure. Malcesine offers lake walks, castle exploration, and magic shows. Bardolino boasts waterparks and theme parks, while La Rocca beckons with camping and outdoor activities.</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">All Italy Holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/6513a747ea8a46b899cfd4357ca2743b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6513a747ea8a46b899cfd4357ca2743b}" title="Italy" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Italy Deals</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Our Top Family Resorts in Italy</h3>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105476/adobestock_479215650.jpg" alt="selva family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/aa04373efe6247f697db697bd6026583" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Selva offers mountain fun for the whole family. Seek adventure playgrounds and wildlife together. Teens thrive with zip lining, hiking, mini-golf, mountain biking, and cycling.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/0acad4ee51f64149a55abd08599b4494" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0acad4ee51f64149a55abd08599b4494}" title="Hotel Pozzamanigoni">Hotel Pozzamanigoni</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella">Hotel Rodella</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Selva</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105477/malcesine-scaligero-castle.jpg" alt="malcesine family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/c5a7eff15ff34e51934dcce1836e6f0a" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>In Malcesine, enjoy beautiful family-friendly walks overlooking the lake, explore Scaligero castle, mini-golf, and museums, and from July 13th to 24th, treat children to magic shows at the 'Padre Mario Casella Gardens.'</p>
<p>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/e647d3120e5c40fa8c337a86bfee1937" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e647d3120e5c40fa8c337a86bfee1937}" title="Hotel Majestic Palace">Hotel Majestic Palace</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/052d6d3d18454435806b717731bfe72b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/052d6d3d18454435806b717731bfe72b}" title="Hotel Excelsior Bay">Hotel Excelsior Bay</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Malcesine</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105482/adobestock_485898626.jpg" alt="bardolino family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/ba732e518673429d86142e9f9d3fe0dd" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Bardolino offers lots of family excitement, from waterparks and theme parks to the thrilling Movieland. Step into nature at La Rocca: camp under the stars, hike its trails, or enjoy paddleboarding and canoeing.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/6972839d41d147188b2b7d3a308ffe3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6972839d41d147188b2b7d3a308ffe3a}" title="Aqualux Hotel Spa Suite &amp; Terme">Aqualux Hotel Spa &amp; Suite</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c85ff8ee0bc44bee8157ff1b59821c85" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c85ff8ee0bc44bee8157ff1b59821c85}" title="Hotel Bisesti">Hotel Bisesti</a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Bardolino</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105489/microsoftteams-image-8-png-1.jpg" alt="switzerland family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/7b25f6e30b4e4e13b3cb8539fb133647" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2 id="switzerland" class="c-card__content">Switzerland Family Holidays</h2>
<div class="c-card__content">Switzerland offers plenty of family adventures: thrilling activities, scenic train rides, pram-friendly hikes, playgrounds, and convenient transport for stress-free exploration.</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">All Switzerland Holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Switzerland Deals</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Our Top Family Resorts in Switzerland</h3>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105485/eiger-express-eiger-sommer-blumenwiese-4.jpg" alt="grindelwald family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/d8c6a6374bc446718868b43d84a2bab9" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Grindelwald offers thrills and relaxation for all ages against stunning Alpine backdrops. Explore exciting day trips, zip lines, and mountain carts on Grindelwald First, or enjoy a leisurely toboggan run and zip line at Pfingstegg.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/f23e91acf64d48939f54f05b0aa723e2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f23e91acf64d48939f54f05b0aa723e2}" title="Eiger Lodge">Eiger Lodge</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c0cd670ad24d4d409a4f1331a1677937" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0cd670ad24d4d409a4f1331a1677937}" title="Hotel Belvedere">Hotel Belvedere</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/518cc472770341548f0da194220efeeb}" title="Romantik Hotel Schweizerhof">Romantik Hotel Schweizwerhof</a><a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella"></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Grindelwald</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105487/davos-_-klosters-2.jpg" alt="Davos Klosters family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/59ff3ade191f46d0a7576ea1c510a56d" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Davos &amp; Klosters offers double the Alpine fun with easy connections between resorts. Explore pram-friendly hikes, playgrounds, and the scenic Bernina Express train – perfect for families with young children. Older kids will love the adventure park, toboggan run, pump tracks, scootering, mini-golf, and aquatic centre with a waterslide.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/84e3f32dc4d644738235556322e16a99" href="/{localLink:umb://document/84e3f32dc4d644738235556322e16a99}" title="Hotel Silvretta Park">Silvretta Park Hotel</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e}" title="Klosters" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Klosters</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105488/observation-deck-in-interlaken_adobestock_133565810.jpg" alt="Interlaken family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/9c342571c139493eb0d289ba6e29f953" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p><span>Interlaken is your gateway to adventure, with a central station for daily explorations. Getting around is a breeze with trains, buses, and cableways. Plus, enjoy unlimited travel with the Interlaken Guest Card.</span></p>
<p>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/8a732f156c174b128f8f1da58ac0b10c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8a732f156c174b128f8f1da58ac0b10c}" title="Hotel Metropole">Hotel Metropole</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c119baf409ff416eaeea1addc52ab0ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c119baf409ff416eaeea1addc52ab0ab}" title="Hotel Stella">Hotel Stella</a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Interlaken</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13103362/adobestock_74245814.jpg" alt="france family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/72341c7d3caa4a7bb33a9334b9ebde3b" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2 id="france" class="c-card__content">France Family Holidays</h2>
<div class="c-card__content">France is perfect for active families. In Chamonix, dive into adventure parks and scenic walks. Morzine offers mini-golf, climbing parks, and the handy Morzine Multipass for discounts and free travel.</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">All France Holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/b04e006ef1604b9e93eb0563af7f0cf8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b04e006ef1604b9e93eb0563af7f0cf8}" title="France" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">France Deals</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Our Top Family Resorts in France</h3>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13105475/chamonix_summer_adobestock_540773290.jpg" alt="chamonix family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/2d4635cb447d4f45b0adf203688a9b60" /></p>
<div class="c-card__content">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a></h4>
<p><span>Chamonix is the perfect spot for an active family. With adventure parks, leisure parks and plenty of walking, there's not shortage of kids activities and family fun.</span></p>
<p><span>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/f8ff2a32fb6340c8b8b770749ac5b27e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f8ff2a32fb6340c8b8b770749ac5b27e}" title="Cristal de Jade Residence">Residence Cristal de Jade</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Chamonix</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13105472/microsoftteams-imagepng-1.jpg" alt="morzine family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/37a74e6106d741659fa7e03317205cd6" /></p>
<div class="c-card__content">
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a></h4>
<p><span>Morzine offers mini-golf, scenic walks, and exciting climbing parks. The Morzine Multipass provides discounts on local attractions and free travel on some local routes.</span></p>
<p><span>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe2634eb5e649179ea3ec16b3c6747a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe2634eb5e649179ea3ec16b3c6747a}" title="Hotel Le Cret">Hotel Le Cret</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac}" title="Hotel Champs Fleuris">Hotel Champs Fleuris</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Morzine</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105483/adobestock_102087722.jpg" alt="slovenia family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/70648e6381e34e398e900ef3440d0673" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2 id="slovenia" class="c-card__content">Slovenia Family Holidays</h2>
<div class="c-card__content">Slovenia is a fantastic choice for families, offering peaceful villages, exciting water activities, fascinating history to explore, and stunning natural scenery for unforgettable adventures together.</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">All Slovenia Holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/a3c4877767844f3d89ad8e5165020482" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a3c4877767844f3d89ad8e5165020482}" title="Slovenia" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Slovenia Deals</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Our Top Family Resorts in Slovenia</h3>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105479/adobestock_171657974.jpg" alt="Kranjska Gora family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/5a6bed256db74e5187c808ecfece538c" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Kranjska Gora, a peaceful village, is perfect for families seeking tranquility with many walking routes and nearby attractions. Enjoy summer tobogganing at Planica Nordic Centre.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba}" title="Hotel Kompas">Hotel Kompas</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/4ed013e224da49958546ddb8415ef8af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4ed013e224da49958546ddb8415ef8af}" title="Hotel Spik">Hotel Spik</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Kranjska Gora</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105480/adobestock_526994142.jpg" alt="lake bled family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/d09eb95c4d4e4c099fb384b0ed842594" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Lake Bled is ideal for families who enjoy water activities and exploring historical sites. Try canoeing, paddleboarding, swimming, and visiting Bled Island and castle.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotels: <a data-udi="umb://document/94de03fc3b9f42eaadf51b5041aee5ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94de03fc3b9f42eaadf51b5041aee5ac}" title="Hotel Rikli Balance">Hotel Rikli Balance</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/7da02416d69d4cefb0f91e9512835dc5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7da02416d69d4cefb0f91e9512835dc5}" title="Hotel Astoria">Hotel Astoria</a></p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Lake Bled</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105481/adobestock_80722318.jpg" alt="lake bohinj" data-udi="umb://media/51186711d7934f8b86151194af4965a3" /></div>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a></h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Lake Bohinj offers picturesque views, easy access to Lake Bled, mountain lookouts, and quiet beaches for fun family adventures.</p>
<p>Recommended Hotel: <a data-udi="umb://document/03d8245538284121b5de9457ff5eb3be" href="/{localLink:umb://document/03d8245538284121b5de9457ff5eb3be}" title="Bohinj ECO Hotel">Eco Hotel Bohinj</a></p>
<p><span><a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Lake Bohinj</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-image">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13105490/adobestock_195474233.jpg" alt="andorra family holidays" data-udi="umb://media/5c75a42a4a2b4b61bf959aba5a62ff36" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2 id="andorra" class="c-card__content">Andorra Family Holidays</h2>
<div class="c-card__content"><span>Arinsal is perfect for families seeking outdoor adventure. Located in the Pyrenees near Comapedrosa National Park, it offers endless trails and stunning scenery. Enjoy leisure parks, nearby cities, or challenge yourselves with family hikes to fantastic viewpoints.</span></div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/8eccec3a0de74863832b485ee830396a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8eccec3a0de74863832b485ee830396a}" title="Arinsal" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Arinsal Holidays</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/fdb9db516d8249c4af16bfbedf3294e0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fdb9db516d8249c4af16bfbedf3294e0}" title="Andorra" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Andorra Deals</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
